{"article_id":"qDwRYDazRD7oC2cn","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Romney Says","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"Mandate 's A Tax ,","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"But Also Sides With Justices","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"Who Say","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"It 's Not","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"There are many stories this morning about what Republican presidential candidate Mitt Romney said to CBS News on Wednesday .","depth":3},{"id":6,"text":"The conventional wisdom is that he reversed his own campaign 's view","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"to say","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"that the so-called individual mandate in the 2010 health care overhaul is a tax , not a penalty .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"There 's attention","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"being paid to what he said to CBS","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"because many in the news media , such as The Associated Press , conclude","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"that :","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"`` Romney 's comments amounted to a shift in position .","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"Earlier in the week , senior adviser Eric Fehrnstrom said","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"Romney viewed the mandate as a penalty , a fee or a fine - not a tax . ''","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"And whether it 's a penalty or a tax is important to the Romney campaign","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"because as governor of Massachusetts he signed into law a health care bill","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"that included a mandate","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"- one","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"that 's been considered a penalty , not a tax .","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"In effect , he 's now saying","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"that the law","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"he signed","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"is n't a tax ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"but that the law","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"President Obama signed","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"is .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"Just what did Romney say to CBS ?","depth":4},{"id":29,"text":"Here are his own words :","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"`` Well , the Supreme Court has the final word .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"And their final word is that Obamacare is a tax .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"So it 's a tax .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"They decided","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"it was constitutional .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"So it is a tax","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"and it 's constitutional .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"That 's the final word .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"That 's what it is . ...","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"`` I said","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"that I agreed with the dissent ,","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"and the dissent made it very clear","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"that they felt it","depth":15},{"id":43,"text":"[ the health care law ]","depth":15},{"id":44,"text":"was unconstitutional .","depth":14},{"id":45,"text":"But the dissent lost .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"It 's in the minority .","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"And so now the Supreme Court has spoken .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"`` There 's no way around that .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"You can try and say","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"you wished","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"they would have decided in a different way ,","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"but they did n't .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"They concluded","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"it was a tax .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"That 's what it is . ''","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"A reading of what the dissenting justices said about last week 's ruling on the health care overhaul shows","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"that they do not believe","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"the mandate is a tax .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"`` There is simply no way ...","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"to escape what Congress enacted :","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"a mandate","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"that individuals maintain minimum essential coverage ,","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"enforced by a penalty . ''","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"So the bottomline from Romney 's comments to CBS is that he 's saying","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"the mandate is a tax","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"because the majority of justices on the Supreme Court say so .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"He did n't specifically say","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"that he agrees with them .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"In fact , he said","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"he agrees with the justices","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"who believe otherwise","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"and that the law is unconstitutional . ``","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"Romney 's campaign insisted","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"it was not a change","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"because the Republican said","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"he agreed with the justices","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"who dissented","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"and would have ruled the mandate unconstitutional .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"The campaign said","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"Romney agreed","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"it is a tax","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"simply because the court determines the 'law of the land . ' ``","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":165,"left":87,"right":164,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":84,"right":86,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":84,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":86,"left":2,"right":85,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":164,"left":109,"right":163,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":5,"right":108,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":89,"right":107,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":6,"right":88,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":88,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":107,"left":100,"right":106,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"